::Bazooka::

    Stumbling end over end down the cliff he came across, Bazooka tries to 
stop himself. It doesn't work. Finally he lands at the bottom on many rocks. 
His axe had gotten loose in the fall and slams down hext to him in a rock. 
All the wound he has recived since activation have taken a toll on him, after 
a land slide and the mutiple shots from autoguns he is starting fade. He 
looks to his weapon to take his life and sees the rock spliting open to 
reveal a small, yet harmful when in robot mode, amout of Energon. He can feel 
the stasis lock comming over him.
    "Bbbbeastt mmooo...." He mutters but not all comes out. Slowly he 
fades....
